246
00:13:02.700 --> 00:13:05.940
Thank you, Mr. Chair. Thank you very much for your substantive submission.

247
00:13:07.780 --> 00:13:11.540
I gleaned that your number one concern is about

248
00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:14.500
