251
00:13:20.960 --> 00:13:23.280
Not just biopesticides, but a whole range of chemicals.

252
00:13:23.420 --> 00:13:25.700
But in particular, biopesticides tend to be

253
00:13:26.640 --> 00:13:29.320
safer for the environment because they are a more natural source.

254
00:13:29.380 --> 00:13:32.820
So that's, yeah, one of the key reasons we are interested in that source.

255
00:13:33.780 --> 00:13:37.280
You also, on page 15,

256
00:13:38.100 --> 00:13:41.240
